{"tid":82673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖］求救Facebook 比人del負皮review","createTime":"2017-01-16T06:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T14:47:55.000Z","uid":50330,"like":7,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"435331ee1815f1de1baca25dc7b0a31e3955bd54","tid":82673,"uid":50330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:42:34.000Z","msg":"係咁的 我係個羽毛球page 上面留左幾個負皮 因為個球會教練個仔係個騙子 呃左我同好多人錢 點知佢即時滅聲<br />\n叫幾十個人比五星佢個page <br />\n我d負皮就比佢河蟹左 <br />\n想問下點解review 都可以delete 有乜方法？<br />\n<br />\n全部review 都係尋日<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPMYjyKNiCBytukWrKGU2xdbin62BU1erVGVVfEFf8JE5?filename=QU571OU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQU571OU.jpg&h=ed18dda8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/16/005208_a754a24fb3f2d2d29f059ec93bef89f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2F005208_a754a24fb3f2d2d29f059ec93bef89f8.jpg&h=07e7519a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/16/005209_a754a24fb3f2d2d29f059ec93bef89f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2F005209_a754a24fb3f2d2d29f059ec93bef89f8.jpg&h=eff0c13b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbCE6KeqMG2hUYT1sDqX3UcwsJ5Uiix7LTz5asey8wxgz?filename=x526LyW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx526LyW.jpg&h=2976062c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地仲想反屈我勒索加黑客 <br />\n但我由頭到尾無叫過佢比錢 我只係想公開 <br />\n公開既權利我都無咩？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/16/005310_699e0e4a5176281809dd7db736e62c42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2F005310_699e0e4a5176281809dd7db736e62c42.jpg&h=be05e598&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸西老母同個騙子<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdPVNmDeq